      tag="Targeted Attacks"
    />
    <CategoryCard
      icon="🔊"
      title="Stochastic Terrorism"
      body="Trump's rhetoric directly preceded Omar's attack, his response encouraged further attacks by denying the violence was real, then he escalated with ISIS accusations"
      tag="Incitement"
    />
    <CategoryCard
      icon="🛡️"
      title="Protection of Powerful Men"
      body="Trump attacked Collins specifically when she asked about justice for Epstein's victims -- deflecting from accountability for sexual violence"
