    <AlertBanner icon="📋" title="The Pattern of Abuse" variant="amber">
      <ul style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">26+ women with similar stories</strong> spanning 40+ years</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Consistent behavior:</strong> Kissing without consent, groping, forced touching</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Abuse of power:</strong> Many were employees, contestants, or young women in vulnerable positions</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Trump's response pattern:</strong> Deny, attack the accuser's appearance, call them liars, threaten lawsuits</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Trump's own admission:</strong> Access Hollywood tape describes the exact behavior women accuse him of</li>
      </ul>
    </AlertBanner>
