    title="Patterns of Degrading<br>Language Against Women"
    introText="Beyond sexual assault, Trump has spent decades publicly degrading women through appearance attacks, sexual objectification, and dehumanizing language. This section documents his systematic pattern of misogyny."
  />

  <!-- Pattern 1: Appearance-Based Attacks -->
